title: Departure from Area18
entry: Departed Area18 under clear conditions. Quantum drive calibration successful. Crew morale remains high.

title: Yela Encounter
entry: Detected Vanduul scout signatures near Yela. Altered course and maintained radio silence. No engagement.

title: Everus Harbor Docking
entry: Docked at Everus Harbor for hull repairs, fuel replenishment, and crew rotation.

title: Anomalous Scan
entry: Long-range sensors picked up an unidentified anomaly in Stanton. Logged coordinates for future investigation.
